{
  "info": {
    "name": "Plane & Prop - Phase 1 & 2: Auth + User Profiles (15 Endpoints)",
    "description": "Complete Phase 1 (8 Auth endpoints) + Phase 2 (7 User Profile & Admin endpoints): Signup, Verify Email, Signin, Refresh, Signout, Resend OTP, Password Reset, Get Profile, Update Profile, Public Profile, Admin User List, Admin Get User, Admin Update User, Admin Update Status",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "PHASE 1️⃣ - Authentication",
      "description": "8 Authentication endpoints - Complete auth flow",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1️⃣ Signup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', jsonData.data.userId);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userEmail', jsonData.data.email);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userName', jsonData.data.fullName);",
                  "    console.log('✅ User created: ' + jsonData.data.userId);",
                  "    console.log('📧 Check email for OTP: ' + jsonData.data.email);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"testuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"full_name\": \"Test User\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/signup",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "signup"]
            },
            "description": "Create new user account with email verification\n\n**Password Requirements:**\n- Minimum 8 characters\n- At least 1 uppercase letter\n- At least 1 number\n- At least 1 special character (!@#$%^&*)\n\n**Response:** 201 Created"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2️⃣ Verify Email",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ Email verified: ' + jsonData.data.email);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/verify-email",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "verify-email"]
            },
            "description": "Verify user's email with OTP from email\n\n**Note:** Replace OTP with actual 6-digit code from email\n\n**Response:** 200 OK"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3️⃣ Signin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('accessToken', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('refreshToken', jsonData.data.refreshToken);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', jsonData.data.user.id);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userRole', jsonData.data.user.role);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Signed in as: ' + jsonData.data.user.email);",
                  "    console.log('🔐 Access Token: ' + jsonData.data.accessToken.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "    console.log('🔄 Refresh Token: ' + jsonData.data.refreshToken.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/signin",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "signin"]
            },
            "description": "User login with verified email and password\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Email must be verified\n- Account must be ACTIVE\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with JWT tokens"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4️⃣ Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('accessToken', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('refreshToken', jsonData.data.refreshToken);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Token refreshed');",
                  "    console.log('🔐 New Access Token: ' + jsonData.data.accessToken.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Refresh access token using refresh token\n\n**When to use:**\n- Access token is expired (15 minutes)\n- Need new access token without re-login\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with new tokens"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5️⃣ Signout",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    console.log('✅ Signed out successfully');",
                  "    console.log('🔐 Refresh token revoked');",
                  "    pm.environment.unset('accessToken');",
                  "    pm.environment.unset('refreshToken');",
                  "    pm.environment.unset('userId');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/signout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "signout"]
            },
            "description": "Sign out user and revoke refresh token\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Valid access token in Authorization header\n- Valid refresh token in body\n\n**Response:** 200 OK"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6️⃣ Resend OTP",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ OTP resent to: ' + jsonData.data.email);",
                  "    console.log('📧 Check email for new verification code');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/resend-otp",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "resend-otp"]
            },
            "description": "Resend verification code if user didn't receive original\n\n**Rate Limit:** 3 attempts per email per hour\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with confirmation message"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "7️⃣ Forgot Password",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    console.log('✅ Password reset email sent');",
                  "    console.log('📧 Check email for reset link (valid for 1 hour)');",
                  "    console.log('💡 If no email received, wait 5 minutes before resending');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/forgot-password",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "forgot-password"]
            },
            "description": "Initiate password reset flow\n\n**Rate Limit:** 5 attempts per email per day\n\n**Security:** Always returns 200 OK (doesn't leak if email exists)\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with confirmation message"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "8️⃣ Reset Password",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    console.log('✅ Password reset successfully');",
                  "    console.log('🔐 All refresh tokens revoked - you must login again');",
                  "    console.log('📧 Confirmation email sent');",
                  "    pm.environment.unset('accessToken');",
                  "    pm.environment.unset('refreshToken');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\",\n  \"token\": \"PASTE_RESET_TOKEN_FROM_EMAIL\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewPassword123!\"\n}\n"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/reset-password",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "reset-password"]
            },
            "description": "Complete password reset using token from email\n\n**Requirements:**\n- Email address\n- Reset token from email (valid for 1 hour)\n- New password (same requirements as signup)\n\n**Side Effects:**\n- All refresh tokens revoked (forces re-login)\n- Confirmation email sent\n\n**Response:** 200 OK"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "PHASE 2️⃣ - User Profiles",
      "description": "7 User profile endpoints - Get, update profiles + Admin user management",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "👤 GET Own Profile",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userProfileId', jsonData.data.id);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Profile fetched: ' + jsonData.data.profile.fullName);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/user/profile",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "profile"]
            },
            "description": "Get current authenticated user's profile\n\n**Protection:** Requires valid access token\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with full profile details"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "✏️ UPDATE Own Profile",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ Profile updated: ' + jsonData.data.fullName);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"bio\": \"Software developer and tech enthusiast\",\n  \"phone\": \"+1234567890\",\n  \"city\": \"San Francisco\",\n  \"country\": \"USA\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/user/profile",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "profile"]
            },
            "description": "Update current user's profile information\n\n**Protection:** Requires valid access token\n\n**Fields:** fullName, bio, phone, city, country (all optional)\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with updated profile"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "👥 GET Public Profile",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ Public profile fetched: ' + jsonData.data.fullName);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/user/{{userId}}/public",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "{{userId}}", "public"]
            },
            "description": "View public profile of any user (limited info)\n\n**Protection:** None - publicly accessible\n\n**Returns:** fullName, bio, avatar, reputation score, join date\n\n**Response:** 200 OK"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "PHASE 2️⃣ - Admin Management",
      "description": "4 Admin-only endpoints - Manage all users, change status, etc.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "📊 LIST All Users",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ Users list fetched: ' + jsonData.data.users.length + ' users');",
                  "    console.log('📄 Page ' + jsonData.data.pagination.page + ' of ' + jsonData.data.pagination.totalPages);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=20&status=ACTIVE&role=STUDENT&sort=createdAt&order=desc",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "users"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                },
                {
                  "key": "status",
                  "value": "ACTIVE"
                },
                {
                  "key": "role",
                  "value": "STUDENT"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sort",
                  "value": "createdAt"
                },
                {
                  "key": "order",
                  "value": "desc"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "List all users with pagination and filters\n\n**Protection:** Admin only - requires ADMIN role\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- page: Page number (default 1)\n- limit: Items per page (default 20, max 100)\n- search: Search in email (optional)\n- status: Filter by status - ACTIVE|INACTIVE|SUSPENDED (optional)\n- role: Filter by role - STUDENT|MENTOR|ADMIN (optional)\n- sort: Sort by - createdAt|email|fullName (default createdAt)\n- order: Sort order - asc|desc (default desc)\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with paginated user list"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "🔍 GET User (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ User fetched: ' + jsonData.data.email);",
                  "    console.log('Role: ' + jsonData.data.role);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "users", "USER_ID_HERE"]
            },
            "description": "Get full profile of any user (admin view)\n\n**Protection:** Admin only - requires ADMIN role\n\n**Note:** Replace USER_ID_HERE with actual UUID\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with complete user info"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "✏️ UPDATE User Profile (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ User profile updated');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Updated Name\",\n  \"bio\": \"Updated bio\",\n  \"city\": \"New City\",\n  \"country\": \"New Country\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "users", "USER_ID_HERE"]
            },
            "description": "Update any user's profile (admin edit)\n\n**Protection:** Admin only - requires ADMIN role\n\n**Note:** Replace USER_ID_HERE with actual UUID\n\n**Fields:** fullName, bio, phone, city, country (all optional)\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with success message"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "🚫 CHANGE User Status (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log('✅ User status changed to: ' + jsonData.data.user.status);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"SUSPENDED\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE/status",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "users", "USER_ID_HERE", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Change user's account status\n\n**Protection:** Admin only - requires ADMIN role\n\n**Note:** Replace USER_ID_HERE with actual UUID\n\n**Status Options:** ACTIVE | INACTIVE | SUSPENDED\n\n**Effects:**\n- ACTIVE: User can login and use platform\n- INACTIVE: User exists but cannot login\n- SUSPENDED: User account suspended (violation, abuse, etc.)\n\n**Response:** 200 OK with updated status"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
